'''特斯拉超級充電'''（Tesla Supercharger）是[[特斯拉_(公司)|特斯拉]]为其[[电动汽车|电动汽车]]產品打造的480伏[[直流電|直流]][[充电桩|快速充电]]技术。特斯拉的超級充電网络于2012年推出。截止到2020年11月8日，特斯拉在全球范围内运营着超过2,016个超級充電站<ref name="supercharger">{{Cite web|title=Superchargers|url=https://supercharge.info/map|accessdate=2018-05-12|author=|date=2019-01-28|first=|work=|publisher=Tesla|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324233336/http://supercharge.info/map|dead-url=no}}</ref>，超过2万个超级充电樁<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tesla on Instagram: "20k Superchargers and counting"|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/CHVq3S_hM3q/|accessdate=2020-11-08|work=Instagram|language=en}}</ref><ref name="supercharger" /> （平均每个超級充電站有10个超级充电樁）。其中北美地区有1042个超級充電站，欧洲地区有559个超級充電站，亚太地区有415个超級充電站<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|title=Superchargers|url=http://supercharge.info/|accessdate=2020-03-20|date=2020-09-01|work=supercharge.info|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161005152802/http://supercharge.info/|archivedate=2016-10-05}}</ref>。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Supercharger Idle Fee|url=https://www.tesla.com/support/supercharger-idle-fee|accessdate=2020-03-31|date=2016-12-16|work=www.tesla.com|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307183711/https://www.tesla.com/support/supercharger-idle-fee|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[特斯拉Model_S|特斯拉Model S]]是第一款能够使用超級充電网络的汽车，随后是[[特斯拉Model_X|特斯拉Model X]]、[[特斯拉Model_3|特斯拉Model 3]]和[[特斯拉Model_Y|特斯拉Model Y]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Tesla ends free Supercharger credit program for Model S and Model X|url=https://electrek.co/2018/11/12/tesla-supercharger-credit-end-model-s-model-x/|accessdate=2020-03-31|author=Lambert|date=2018-11-12|first=Fred|work=[[Electrek|Electrek]]|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210310192458/https://electrek.co/2018/11/12/tesla-supercharger-credit-end-model-s-model-x/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

